    "description": "公元2639年，来源不明的变异机械生命体攻入人类的太空殖民星球。它们盘踞在能源矿区，并夺走了大量能源碎片。失去矿区的掌控权，意味着人类在该星周围作业的宇宙飞船将失去能源补给，所有船员危在旦夕。你将跟随“星途”号母舰，去迎击各个能源星球上的入侵者，夺回赖以生存的能源矿区。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>各具特色的、超巨大的半机械能量异变体BOSS设计，以及它们所释放出的漫天弹幕攻击。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/362a4184aaf409c887b378589127b16b.poster.avif?t=1709861004\" width=496 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/362a4184aaf409c887b378589127b16b.webm?t=1709861004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/362a4184aaf409c887b378589127b16b.mp4?t=1709861004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/1af1c507ff79572128e2eb99f149e768.poster.avif?t=1709861004\" width=496 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/1af1c507ff79572128e2eb99f149e768.webm?t=1709861004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/1af1c507ff79572128e2eb99f149e768.mp4?t=1709861004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>玩家在漫天弹幕之中，通过瞬移功能，进行360°全方位辗转腾挪。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/b5ca6aabddebc758413b045953efa06e.poster.avif?t=1709861004\" width=496 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/b5ca6aabddebc758413b045953efa06e.webm?t=1709861004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/b5ca6aabddebc758413b045953efa06e.mp4?t=1709861004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>玩家可以使用引力弹、浮空雷、量子粉碎等多种强大的技能。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关卡玩法丰富：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>以歼灭巨大boss为目的的主关卡。<br></li><li>以破坏敌方基地为目的的堡垒攻坚战。<br></li><li>被机械生物包围！限时生存挑战。<br></li><li>与拥有与玩家相同技能的敌方精英怪1v1的暗影对决战。<br></li><li>等等。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/c52eba6a7817495a799738166a6d50ff.poster.avif?t=1709861004\" width=496 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/c52eba6a7817495a799738166a6d50ff.webm?t=1709861004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171060/extras/c52eba6a7817495a799738166a6d50ff.mp4?t=1709861004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><a href=\"mailto:联系邮箱：special@xrlinkup.com\">联系邮箱：special@xrlinkup.com</a><br>QQ群：190412060",
